snippet.title: SNES Super Bomberman: Panic Bomber W
snippet.description:
Support Shiryu on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Shiryu
https://www.facebook.com/ShiryuVideoGames/

Bringing "Panic Bomber" home to the 16-bit powerhouse that is the Super Famicom, Hudson added a frantic four player mode to the whole thing. A must have for puzzle game lover. Enjoy!
